orelle official photo (cropped).jpg|100px]]<br/>[[Joseph Morelle|Joe Morelle]]<br/>([[Rochester, New York|Rochester]])\n| {{Party shading/Democratic}} | [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n| November 13, 2018\n| {{Party shading/Democratic}} data-sort-value=-8 | D+8\n| [[File:New York US Congressional District 25 (since 2013).tif|400px|]]\n\n|-\n! {{ushr|NY|26|R}}\n| [[File:Brian Higgins official photo.jpg|100px]]<br/>[[Brian Higgins]]<br/>([[Buffalo, New York|Buffalo]])\n| {{Party shading/Democratic}} | [[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n| January 3, 2005\n| {{Party shading/Democratic}} data-sort-value=-11 | D+11\n| [[File:New York US Congressional District 26 (since 2013).tif|400px|]]\n\n|-\n! {{ushr|NY|27|R}}\n| Vacant\n| \n| \n| {{Party shading/Republican}} data-sort-value=11 | R+11\n| [[File:New York US Congressional District 27 (since 2013).tif|400px|]]\n\n|}\n\n===1789\u20131793: 6 seats===\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Cong<br/>ress\n! colspan=6 | District\n! rowspan=2 | Cong<br/>ress\n|-\n! {{ushr|New York|1|1st}}\n! {{ushr|New York|2|2nd}}\n! {{ushr|New York|3|3rd}}\n! {{ushr|New York|4|4th}}\n! {{ushr|New York|5|5th}}\n! {{ushr|New York|6|6th}}\n\n|- style=\"height:2em\"\n| '''{{USCongressOrdinal|1}}'''<br/>1789\u20131791\n| {{party shading/Anti-Administration}} | [[William Floyd]]<br/>(Anti-Admin)\n| rowspan=3 {{party shading/Pro-Administration}} | [[John Laurance]]<br/>(Pro-Admin)\n| rowspan=3 {{party shading/Pro-Administration}} | [[Egbert Benson]]<br/>(Pro-Admin)\n| {{party shading/Anti-Administration}} | [[John Hathorn]]<br/>(Anti-Admin)\n| rowspan=3 {{party shading/Pro-Administration}} | [[Peter Silvester (1734\u20131808)|Peter Silvester]]<br/>(Pro-Admin)\n| {{party shading/Anti-Administration}} | [[Jeremiah Van Rensselaer]]<br/>(Anti-Admin)\n| '''{{USCongressOrdinal|1}}'''<br/>1789\u20131791\n\n|- style=\"height:2em\"\n| rowspan=2 | '''{{USCongressOrdinal|2}}'''<br/>1791\u20131793\n| 